Package com.gerken.gumbo.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Graph
    Represents a directed graph that is a Storm topology of nodes (spouts and bolts) and edges (streams between components).
    GraphEdge
    Represents an edge in the graph
    GraphNode
    Represents a node in the graph A GraphNode has knowledge of the position of the node with respect to other nodes before and after it in the graph.
    PathSegment
    Represents a segment of the displayable path of an edge.
    WayPoint
    Represents a logical point in the layout of a node or edge and is used primarily to perform a rough layout of the nodes and edges.
